	(48534,6625,2,0,1,0,'Page','2009-01-26 10:08:20','2009-01-26 10:08:41','in-the-beginning','In The Beginning',NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 16px; line-height: normal;\">\n<h2 style=\"color: #4ea3d7; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 18px; margin-left: 0px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 1em; line-height: 120%;\">How It All Began</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>In 1991, three university friends met up for dinner and got to talking. &nbsp;What if they pooled their knowledge, skills and resources and formed a company, developing a service the like of which the world was crying out for? &nbsp;That night&nbsp;was to witness the initial phases of an amazing metamorphosis, transforming these three regular 9-to-fivers into brilliant, but mad, entrepreneurs...</p>\n<h6 style=\"font-family: Georgia, \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif; font-size: 13px; color: #555555; line-height: 1.4em; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 12px; margin-left: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: #666666; font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;\">A</span>nd so, after four years, five months, two weeks and three days the metamorphosis was complete and the business formed by their creative genius was released to the world.</h6>\n</span></p>\n</blockquote>','In The Beginning',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,8,NULL,0,0,'Saved (new)',NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),
