	(49462,6674,10,1,1,1,'Page','2012-05-25 08:28:48','2012-06-29 13:42:50','responsive','Responsive',NULL,'<p>Reduce the width of your browser window to the length of this line.</p>\n<p>The menus and other elements of the page will change to be mobile friendly.</p>\n<p>Or, view this page on your favourite smartphone.</p>\n<p>That\'s called a responsive design, a technique made possible using HTML5. This behaviour is provided by the default SilverStripe 3 theme, named Simple.</p>\n<p><img class=\"left\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/_resampled/resizedimage378567-iPhoneSimple.PNG\" alt=\"iPhone screenshot of Simple\" width=\"378\" height=\"567\"/></p>','Responsive',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,6,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),
	(49463,6682,11,1,1,1,'Page','2012-06-28 13:00:19','2012-06-29 13:44:34','listview','Listview',NULL,'<p>ListView makes finding and updating pages on very large sites considerably easier. In the CMS, while browsing the familiar site tree, click the  Treeview icon. Now you can work with the site tree using filters and paginated lists.</p>\n<p><img class=\"left\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/_resampled/resizedimage699514-listview-509rows-screenshot.png\" alt=\"listview 509rows screenshot\" width=\"699\" height=\"514\"/></p>','Treeview',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6686,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),
