	(49541,6681,7,0,1,0,'Page','2012-05-25 13:52:37','2013-10-04 14:18:27','security-and-audit-trail','Security & Audit Trail',NULL,'<p>Every save made to a page contributes to an audit trail. You can compare old versions with each other and roll back to them in the History Tab.</p>\n<p>A powerful security system allows viewing and editing of pages to be restricted to various users. Users and groups can be created, and this can all provide the basis for secure login areas or more elaborate publishing workflow.</p>\n<p><img class=\"leftAlone\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/_resampled/resizedimage600421-silverstripe-security-page.png\" alt=\"silverstripe security page\" height=\"421\" width=\"600\"/></p>','Security & Audit Trail',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,9,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,7197,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','OnlyTheseUsers',NULL,0,0,0),
