	(49695,6674,20,1,1,1,'Page','2012-05-25 08:28:48','2013-10-21 14:28:23','responsive','Responsive',NULL,'<div class=\"captionImage right\" style=\"width: 338px;\"><br><p class=\"caption right\"> </p>\n</div>\n<p><span class=\"intro\">The Simple theme has been built using responsive styling. This means when you reduce the width of your browser window, the site will adapt to the screen size, a technique made possible using HTML5. </span></p>\n<p>Responsive web design is an approach aimed at crafting sites to provide an optimal viewing experience - easy reading and navigation with minimal resizing, panning, and scrolling - across a wide range of devices (from mobile phones to desktop computer monitors).</p>\n<p>This behaviour is provided by the default with the SilverStripe 3 theme. Alternatively, you can also view this page on your favourite smartphone to see how the theme adjusts to a specific device. The menus and other elements of the page will change to be mobile or tablet friendly.</p>\n<p><img class=\"leftAlone\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/Responsive-SilverStripe.png\" alt=\"Responsive SilverStripe\" width=\"398\" height=\"659\"></p>','Responsive',NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,6678,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),
