	(49721,86,276,1,1,1,'HomePage','2007-10-01 12:47:24','2016-02-15 11:42:48','home','Welcome to the public demo of the SilverStripe CMS','Home','<div id=\"Thanks\">\n<p class=\"intro\" style=\"text-align: left;\">The SilverStripe CMS is an open source web content management system used by governments, businesses, and non-profit organisations around the world. It is a powerful tool for professional web development teams, and web content authors rave about how easy it is to use.</p>\n<p>[embed width=\"600\" height=\"337\" class=\"leftAlone\" thumbnail=\"http://b.vimeocdn.com/ts/312/000/312000748_1280.jpg?r\"]https://vimeo.com/44848958[/embed]</p>\n<h3>SilverStripe CMS</h3>\n<p>As a platform, the SilverStripe CMS is used to build websites, intranets and web applications. The modern architecture of the SilverStripe CMS allows organisations to keep pace with innovation on the web. The SilverStripe CMS enables websites and applications to contain stunning design, great content as well as compelling interactive and social functions.</p>\n<h3>SilverStripe Framework</h3>\n<p>Besides a powerful and intuitive content authoring application, the SilverStripe CMS contains a powerful PHP5-based programming framework. The SilverStripe Framework brings immense flexibility and ease in customising your site and provides fundamentals such as security models, workflow, caching and multiple language and subsite support.</p>\n</div>',NULL,'this is my test of this website template...',NULL,1,1,NULL,0,1,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',NULL,0,0,0),
	(49722,7198,7,1,1,1,'Page','2013-10-04 13:59:38','2016-02-15 12:48:07','silverstripe-framework','SilverStripe Framework',NULL,'<p><span class=\"intro\">Besides a powerful and intuitive content authoring application, the SilverStripe CMS contains a powerful PHP5-based programming framework. The SilverStripe Framework brings immense flexibility and ease in customising your site and provides fundamentals such as security models, workflow, caching as well as multiple language and sub-site support.</span></p>\n<h3>Under the hood</h3>\n<p>Behind the clean CMS and website presentation sits <a title=\"SilverStripe Framework\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/software/framework/\">SilverStripe Framework</a>. Website developers use the framework to write code to create templates, logic and tailor how the CMS works. Developers get the power and flexibility of (object oriented PHP 5.3+) code, designers get the freedom of HTML5 and CSS, and content authors get the simplicity of a tailored CMS.</p>\n<p><img class=\"leftAlone\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/silverstripe-php-code-sample.png\" alt=\"silverstripe php code sample\" width=\"298\" height=\"162\"></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,2,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),
	(49723,7199,10,1,1,1,'Page','2013-10-04 14:02:04','2016-02-15 12:49:54','silverstripe-community','SilverStripe Community',NULL,'<p class=\"intro\"><a title=\"Visit SilverStripe.org\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org\" target=\"_blank\">SilverStripe.org</a> is the central hub for the community surrounding the SilverStripe CMS and Framework. The SilverStripe community offers a broad range of support for individuals, companies and organisations as well as for those supporting the future development of the CMS and Framework.</p>\n<p><img class=\"leftAlone\" title=\"\" src=\"assets/Uploads/_resampled/ResizedImage974451-community.png\" alt=\"SilverStripe Community\" width=\"795\" height=\"368\"></p>\n<p><a title=\"SilverStripe forums\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/forums/\">Discussion forums</a><br><a title=\"Community showcase\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/community/showcase/\">Community showcase</a><br><a title=\"SilverStripe Meetups\" href=\"http://www.meetup.com/find/?keywords=SilverStripe&amp;radius=Infinity&amp;userFreeform=Wellington%2C+New+Zealand&amp;mcName=Wellington%2C+NZ&amp;lat=-41.300003&amp;lon=174.7833&amp;sort=default\" target=\"_blank\">SilverStripe meetups</a><br><a title=\"Developer directory\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/community/developer-and-partner-directory/\">Developer directory</a></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,3,NULL,0,0,NULL,NULL,'Anyone','LoggedInUsers',0,0,102,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Inherit','Inherit',NULL,0,0,0),
	(49724,7201,6,1,1,1,'Page','2013-10-08 10:16:22','2016-02-15 13:04:08','support','SilverStripe Support',NULL,'<p><span class=\"intro\">The SilverStripe community are passionate people, making the web a better place through better code, user experiences and engagement.</span></p>\n<p><strong>SilverStripe open source support </strong>– <a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org\">silverstripe.org</a><a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/help-and-support/\"><strong><br></strong></a>If you are looking for help with our open source product, refer to the following sections on our open source community website.<br>You can find:</p>\n<ul><li><a title=\"SilverStripe Developer documentation\" href=\"http://docs.silverstripe.org\">documentation for developers</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Community resources\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/community/\">community resources</a> for developers including forums, realtime conversations, mailing lists</li>\n<li><a title=\"SilverStripe Developer mailing list\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/silverstripe-dev\">discussions</a> of core development topics</li>\n<li>the <a title=\"Developer Directory\" href=\"http://www.silverstripe.org/community/developer-and-partner-directory/\">Developer Directory</a>, helping to source the right developer for the job wherever you are in the world</li>\n<li><span class=\"screen-name\">community <a title=\"SilverStripe Meetups\" href=\"http://silverstripe.meetup.com/\">events and meetups</a> throughout the world</span></li>\n</ul><p><strong>CMS user help</strong> – <a href=\"http://userhelp.silverstripe.org/framework/en/\">userhelp.silverstripe.org</a><br>Resources for website editors, CMS users and administrators.</p>\n<p><strong>Professional support by SilverStripe Ltd.</strong> – <a href=\"http://www.silverstripe.com\">silverstripe.com<br></a>Whatever you need, no matter how big or small, SilverStripe Ltd. can help find a solution that works best for you.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,NULL,0,5,